<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>High-Risk Sign-In — Session Revoked</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f4f6f9; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color: #1a1a2e; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 32px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626 0%, #991b1b 100%); padding: 36px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; color: #fff; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.3px; }
    .header p  { margin: 8px 0 0; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-size: 14px; }
    .icon { font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .body { padding: 36px 40px; }
    .greeting { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .intro { color: #555; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .revoked-banner { background: #fef2f2; border: 2px solid #dc2626; border-radius: 10px; padding: 18px 22px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .revoked-banner strong { display: block; color: #991b1b; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .revoked-banner span { color: #7f1d1d; font-size: 14px; }
    .info-card { background: #fff1f2; border: 1px solid #fecdd3; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .info-card h3 { margin: 0 0 14px; font-size: 13px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; color: #9f1239; font-weight: 700; }
    .info-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; padding: 6px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #fecdd3; font-size: 14px; }
    .info-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .info-label { color: #78716c; font-weight: 500; min-width: 110px; }
    .info-value { color: #1c1917; font-weight: 600; text-align: right; word-break: break-word; }
    .reasons-section { margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .reasons-section h3 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #991b1b; }
    .reason-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 10px 14px; background: #fee2e2; border-left: 3px solid #dc2626; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 14px; color: #44403c; font-weight: 500; }
    .cta-section { text-align: center; margin: 28px 0; }
    .cta-section p { font-size: 15px; color: #555; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .btn-secure { display: inline-block; padding: 16px 36px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626, #991b1b); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.3px; }
    .steps-box { background: #fafafa; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .steps-box h3 { margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; }
    .step { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 14px; color: #374151; }
    .step-num { background: #dc2626; color: #fff; width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
    .footer { background: #f8fafc; padding: 24px 40px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
    .footer p { margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6; }
    .footer a { color: #6366f1; text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="icon">🚨</div>
      <h1>High-Risk Sign-In Detected</h1>
      <p>Your session was automatically revoked for your protection.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="body">
      <div class="greeting">Hi {{displayName}},</div>
      <p class="intro">
        We detected a high-risk sign-in attempt on your MeriGauMata account.
        For your security, the session was <strong>automatically revoked</strong> before it could be used.
      </p>

      <div class="revoked-banner">
        <strong>🔒 Session Automatically Revoked</strong>
        <span>The suspicious session has been terminated. You are currently safe.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="info-card">
        <h3>Suspicious Sign-In Details</h3>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Time</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{signedInAt}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">IP Address</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{ipAddress}}</span>
        </div>
        {{#if city}}
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Location</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{city}}{{#if region}}, {{region}}{{/if}} ({{country}})</span>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Device</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{deviceType}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">OS</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{os}} {{osVersion}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Browser</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{browser}} {{browserVersion}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Risk Level</span>
          <span class="info-value" style="color: #dc2626;">HIGH RISK</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      {{#if suspicionReasons}}
      <div class="reasons-section">
        <h3>Why this was flagged as HIGH RISK:</h3>
        {{#each suspicionReasons}}
        <div class="reason-item">🚨 {{this}}</div>
        {{/each}}
      </div>
      {{/if}}

      <div class="steps-box">
        <h3>Immediate steps to secure your account:</h3>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">1</div>
          <span>Change your password immediately — use a strong, unique password.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">2</div>
          <span>Enable two-factor authentication if you haven't already.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">3</div>
          <span>Review your active sessions and revoke any you don't recognise.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">4</div>
          <span>If you believe your account was compromised, contact our support team.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-section">
        <p>Re-authenticate to restore access and secure your account.</p>
        <a href="{{secureUrl}}" class="btn-secure">🔐 Secure My Account</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        This email was sent by MeriGauMata · <a href="{{frontendUrl}}">merigaumata.com</a><br/>
        You're receiving this because a high-risk sign-in was detected and automatically blocked.<br/>
        © {{year}} MeriGauMata. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
